quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  1,4,"Nsyene Lisiku Lyamalipilo."
  1,5,"Kwele Jikape tukwagalagatila, soni Kwele Jikape tukwaŵenda chikamuchisyo."
  1,6,"Tujongolelani kwitala lyagoloka. ",1:[Chongolo chili patundu paŵili: (a) Chongolo cha Taufîq, chachili chakuumila kwa Allah pe basi. Allah jukasaugula ntima wa mundu kuti ayipochele yakuona. (Kutyoka ku ukafili ni kulupilila Tauhidi). (b) Chongolo cha Irshâd, kupitila mu kulalichila kwa Achimitenga ŵa Allah kwisa soni akuŵilanjila ŵaliose ŵaakuŵilanjilaga ku Usilamu.]
  2,1,"Alif-Lâm-Mîm. ",1:[Asi harufusi ni chimpepe mu isimosimo ya Qur’an. Ni pangali jwine jwaakumanyilila mate gakwe ikaŵeje Allah pe basi.]
  2,2,"Achi ni Chitabu changali kaikasya nkati mwakwe, chongolo cha ŵakun'jogopa (Allah)."
  2,3,"Aŵala ŵakasakulupililaga yangaiona, ni akwimikaga Swala mwakolosya, soni mu ichindu yatwapele akasatolaga."